/* Table: "C_BoothType" */
/*==============================================================*/
create table "C_BoothType"
(
"BoothTypeID" NUMBER(8) not null,
"BoothTypeTypeCode" VARCHAR2(20),
"BoothTypeTypeName" NVARCHAR2(100),
"Enable" INTEGER,
"CreateBy" NUMBER(32),
"CreateTime" TIMESTAMP,
"ModifyBy" NUMBER(32),
"ModifyTime" TIMESTAMP,
constraint PK_C_BOOTHTYPE primary key ("BoothTypeID")
);

0：停用';
